---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';

---

<section id="home" class="relative pt-32 pb-20 md:pt-40 md:pb-28 lg:pt-48 lg:pb-36 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-50/90 to-primary-100/80 mix-blend-multiply"></div>
    <Image 
      src={"/placeholder.svg"} 
      alt="Elegant makeup by Make up Artist" 
      class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      width={1920}
      height={1080}
      quality={90}
    />
  </div>
  
  <div class="container relative z-10">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-primary-700 mb-4 font-light">Maquillaje Profesional</p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-light tracking-wide text-neutral-900 mb-6">
        El arte de realzar tu belleza natural
      </h1>
      <p class="text-neutral-700 font-light max-w-xl mx-auto mb-10 text-base md:text-lg">
        Maquillaje profesional para novias y eventos especiales. Creando looks únicos que resaltan tu belleza natural con un toque de sofisticación.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="#contact" class="bg-primary-500 hover:bg-primary-600 text-white px-8 py-3 text-sm tracking-wider transition-colors">
          RESERVAR CONSULTA
        </a>
        <a href="#gallery" class="border border-neutral-300 hover:border-primary-300 text-neutral-800 px-8 py-3 text-sm tracking-wider transition-colors">
          VER PORTAFOLIO
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>